    .row
      .medium-6.columns
        h1= 'Savory Network'

      .medium-6.columns
        p The Network is the lifeblood of the organization — a global network of entrepreneurial leaders committed to serving their regions with Holistic Management training and implementation support. Our growing network of regional Hubs and Accredited Professionals is taking Holistic Management from theory to practice, with resounding success in real communities.



  #savory-hub(data-magellan-destination='savory-hub')
  section.main
    header.overview-header
      .row
        .medium-3.columns
          h2.section-title Savory Hub
        .medium-9.columns
          p Our goal is to partner with local individuals and organizations to establish self-sustaining Savory Hubs. Hubs provide Holistic Management training and implementation support for farmers, ranchers, and land managers.

    .row
      .small-12.columns
        p By 2025, we will establish 100 Savory Hubs around the world, providing local capacity and infrastructure to train — and support — thousands of practitioners. This will influence the management of 1 billion hectares of land; <em> that's &frac15; of the grasslands of the world.</em>

        h3 Services
        p Supported by Savory Institute, each Savory Hub will be responsible for marketing and implementing the following programs and services for local practitioners, NGOs, and government agencies:


        .key-points
          .keyline
          .row.collapse
            .medium-6.columns.left
              .point
                h4 Professional Training
                p Each Savory Hub will offer training in Farm Planning and Holistic Grazing for both commercial and communal land-based practitioners, as well as NGOs and governments working with pastoralists. It will have access to land that can be used to provide practical hands-on experience as part of the training curriculum. Furthermore, each Hub will offer formal accreditation for professionals who desire to train or consult with practitioners on the implementation of Holistic Management.

              .point
                h4 Project Consulting
                p Each Savory Hub will offer custom holistic training, education, and consulting services to land managers, organizations and governments who are influencing the management of large areas of grasslands or degraded dry lands.

              .point
                h4 Full Spectrum Monitoring
                p Each Savory Hub will offer biological, social, and financial monitoring services to land managers, organizations and governments to ensure long-term sustainability of their projects and initiatives.

            .medium-6.columns.right
              .point
                h4 Educational Programs
                p Each Savory Hub will offer opportunities for local youth and community members to learn more about Holistic Management and the business, policy, and scientific issues involved in sustainable land management.

              .point
                h4 Auditing Services
                p Each Savory Hub will offer auditing services to land managers who are interested in accessing established market incentives or premium prices for their products under specific sustainable land and livestock management standards.

              .point
                h4 Entrepreneurial Incubator
                p Each Savory Hub will serve as a regional incubator for innovative land-based enterprises that could enhance triple bottom line returns to land managers, including innovative approaches to monetizing ecosystem services.




