          i.fa.fa-shopping-cart
          | Pay Exit Fee


        hr
        h3 Renew Accreditation
        p If you are an approved Accredited Professional with Savory and you wish to sign up and pay for your annual renewal fee, you may do so here. If you are interested in <em>becoming</em> an accredited professional with Savory, credit will be given for participation in our <a href='/platform/#online-ed'>Online Education</a> — that is where you should begin.
        a.btn-primary(href='http://savory-institute.myshopify.com/collections/accredited-professional-subscriptions', target="_blank")
          i.fa.fa-shopping-cart
          | Renew Accreditation
